1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 8]

2
00:00:32,768 --> 00:00:34,007
Which young master are you calling?

3
00:00:38,208 --> 00:00:39,327
Young Master!

4
00:00:39,968 --> 00:00:40,967
Young Master!

5
00:00:55,888 --> 00:00:57,607
Ye Zhiqiu, calm down.

6
00:01:44,568 --> 00:01:45,727
I'll wait for you...

7
00:01:47,528 --> 00:01:48,927
until I'm certain.

8
00:02:16,528 --> 00:02:17,967
He sent me back.

9
00:02:20,568 --> 00:02:21,207
Fifth Concubine,

10
00:02:21,368 --> 00:02:22,207
you're awake?

11
00:02:24,488 --> 00:02:25,207
Nanxi,

12
00:02:25,768 --> 00:02:26,687
when did you arrive?

13
00:02:28,088 --> 00:02:28,687
Just now.

14
00:02:30,368 --> 00:02:32,087
The master is in high spirits today.

15
00:02:32,328 --> 00:02:33,607
All the servants working in the courtyard

16
00:02:33,608 --> 00:02:34,727
received rewards.

17
00:02:36,088 --> 00:02:37,447
The master specifically asked me

18
00:02:37,448 --> 00:02:38,607
to deliver this to you.

19
00:02:39,088 --> 00:02:40,327
High-end jewelry bought at

20
00:02:40,328 --> 00:02:41,087
a Western auction house.

21
00:02:41,088 --> 00:02:42,167
Only one set in existence.

22
00:02:42,648 --> 00:02:44,127
Such valuable jewelry...

23
00:02:44,488 --> 00:02:46,127
Why wasn't it sent to Third Concubine?

24
00:02:48,208 --> 00:02:49,487
Three years.

25
00:02:49,688 --> 00:02:51,207
The master has finally succeeded

26
00:02:51,248 --> 00:02:52,087
with you.

27
00:02:52,968 --> 00:02:53,727
Fifth Concubine,

28
00:02:54,088 --> 00:02:55,207
you're truly remarkable.

29
00:03:05,088 --> 00:03:06,447
Zhiqiu...

30
00:03:20,888 --> 00:03:21,807
what is this letter?

31
00:03:22,728 --> 00:03:24,047
The postman came this morning.

32
00:03:24,048 --> 00:03:26,047
Said it's a bill from the dye house for you.

33
00:03:26,608 --> 00:03:27,927
Did you order new fabric?

34
00:03:29,128 --> 00:03:30,447
A bill from the dye house?

35
00:03:31,368 --> 00:03:32,487
I didn't buy anything.

36
00:03:35,288 --> 00:03:40,487
[Your order is in and ready for pickup. Please collect it as soon as possible.]

37
00:04:09,648 --> 00:04:10,287
Come out.

38
00:04:10,568 --> 00:04:11,287
I know it's you

39
00:04:16,168 --> 00:04:18,127
Seems you still remember my handwriting.

40
00:04:20,048 --> 00:04:21,167
Do you have new clues?

41
00:04:26,128 --> 00:04:26,767
This is An He's

42
00:04:26,768 --> 00:04:28,087
lodging receipt from Xin County

43
00:04:28,408 --> 00:04:29,047
three years ago

44
00:04:29,128 --> 00:04:30,287
one week before Chuxue's incident.

45
00:04:30,368 --> 00:04:31,527
An He returned to Peixiang.

46
00:04:31,648 --> 00:04:32,327
Several months later,

47
00:04:32,408 --> 00:04:33,407
she secretly gave birth to a child.

48
00:04:33,648 --> 00:04:34,727
Confirmed no time to commit the crime.

49
00:04:35,128 --> 00:04:36,327
It eliminates her suspicion.

50
00:04:38,288 --> 00:04:38,807
Did you find out

51
00:04:38,808 --> 00:04:40,087
whose child this is?

52
00:04:40,168 --> 00:04:41,127
No one knows.

53
00:04:41,888 --> 00:04:43,207
Marshal Lu and An He

54
00:04:43,368 --> 00:04:44,607
knew each other for less than a year.

55
00:04:45,288 --> 00:04:46,287
From what I know,

56
00:04:47,128 --> 00:04:47,847
Marshal Lu

57
00:04:48,248 --> 00:04:48,847
simply didn't know

58
00:04:48,848 --> 00:04:50,007
about this child's existence.

59
00:04:54,408 --> 00:04:55,767
I'll keep investigating for you.

60
00:04:57,248 --> 00:04:58,287
Thank you.

61
00:05:06,968 --> 00:05:07,607
This

62
00:05:07,608 --> 00:05:08,887
is what I'm giving you based on

63
00:05:08,888 --> 00:05:10,247
current market rates for private detectives

64
00:05:10,248 --> 00:05:10,967
at newspapers.

65
00:05:12,288 --> 00:05:13,447
If you feel it's insufficient,

66
00:05:13,728 --> 00:05:14,647
you can ask for more.

67
00:05:16,768 --> 00:05:17,327
Xiaoman...

68
00:05:17,488 --> 00:05:18,487
What do you mean by this?

69
00:05:20,288 --> 00:05:21,087
I just

70
00:05:21,488 --> 00:05:21,967
don't like people

71
00:05:21,968 --> 00:05:23,367
helping me out of the blue.

72
00:05:23,368 --> 00:05:24,727
Do you think my investigation for you

73
00:05:25,128 --> 00:05:26,047
and all of this

74
00:05:26,288 --> 00:05:27,327
is just a transaction?

75
00:05:30,168 --> 00:05:31,287
After all, you even

76
00:05:31,408 --> 00:05:32,687
went to An He's hometown for me.

77
00:05:33,168 --> 00:05:33,727
You've done so much for me.

78
00:05:33,728 --> 00:05:35,167
You can think of it as me making amends.

79
00:05:35,368 --> 00:05:36,487
Think of it as my atonement.

80
00:05:37,288 --> 00:05:38,287
Or consider it

81
00:05:38,288 --> 00:05:39,847
my way of protecting you.

82
00:05:40,528 --> 00:05:41,767
But could you please not

83
00:05:42,048 --> 00:05:43,767
treat my efforts like a transaction?

84
00:05:46,768 --> 00:05:47,527
Is that okay?

85
00:05:52,328 --> 00:05:52,967
Right.

86
00:05:57,408 --> 00:05:59,247
This is what you should've done three years ago.

87
00:06:25,528 --> 00:06:27,127
Seems An He retired back then

88
00:06:27,408 --> 00:06:28,807
because of this child.

89
00:06:29,288 --> 00:06:29,967
Chuxue,

90
00:06:29,968 --> 00:06:30,647
Eldest Young Master,

91
00:06:30,848 --> 00:06:31,927
and that opera performer

92
00:06:32,408 --> 00:06:33,567
had an entangled relationship.

93
00:06:33,728 --> 00:06:35,527
They were once best friends.

94
00:06:35,848 --> 00:06:36,847
Later they broke ties.

95
00:06:37,568 --> 00:06:39,487
Could this child be Zhou Yimo's?

96
00:06:40,288 --> 00:06:41,527
If you came to the Zhou residence

97
00:06:41,528 --> 00:06:42,687
seeking revenge,

98
00:06:43,288 --> 00:06:44,487
then could you tell me

99
00:06:45,408 --> 00:06:47,607
what secrets surround Chuxue's death?

100
00:06:48,288 --> 00:06:49,807
Who holds deep hatred for you?

101
00:06:50,288 --> 00:06:51,607
What evidence do you have?

102
00:06:51,848 --> 00:06:53,007
I can help you!

103
00:06:53,168 --> 00:06:54,687
I caused Chuxue's death.

104
00:06:56,048 --> 00:06:56,967
Don't say that.

105
00:06:57,888 --> 00:06:59,127
I'm also to blame.

106
00:07:02,608 --> 00:07:03,927
Could it be that from the very beginning

107
00:07:04,368 --> 00:07:05,847
Zhou Yimo has been deceiving me?

108
00:07:06,368 --> 00:07:07,047
Fifth concubine!

109
00:07:09,488 --> 00:07:10,207
What a coincidence.

110
00:07:11,368 --> 00:07:12,207
Second Young Master,

111
00:07:13,168 --> 00:07:14,167
what are you doing here?

112
00:07:18,568 --> 00:07:20,327
Father wants to have some clothes made for you,

113
00:07:20,848 --> 00:07:22,287
so I came to look at fabrics.

114
00:07:22,848 --> 00:07:23,727
He wouldn't have seen

115
00:07:23,728 --> 00:07:25,047
me with Yu Shi'an, would he?

116
00:07:26,328 --> 00:07:26,807
Fifth concubine.

117
00:07:27,368 --> 00:07:28,167
What's wrong?

118
00:07:31,328 --> 00:07:32,327
You came to buy fabric,

119
00:07:32,728 --> 00:07:34,167
but I don't see you carrying any.

120
00:07:40,528 --> 00:07:41,127
I saw some

121
00:07:41,128 --> 00:07:42,367
saddening scenes,

122
00:07:43,808 --> 00:07:44,927
so I lost interest.

123
00:07:46,288 --> 00:07:47,287
What scenes?

124
00:07:49,048 --> 00:07:49,807
I saw

125
00:07:52,488 --> 00:07:53,887
you and Captain Yu

126
00:07:54,808 --> 00:07:55,887
meeting secretly.

127
00:08:01,048 --> 00:08:02,127
Oh?

128
00:08:02,888 --> 00:08:04,167
Captain Yu and I

129
00:08:04,368 --> 00:08:05,847
do have some past connections.

130
00:08:06,048 --> 00:08:07,647
But we just happened to meet at the fabric store.

131
00:08:07,848 --> 00:08:09,047
It's not what you think.

132
00:08:11,808 --> 00:08:12,967
What do I think?

133
00:08:14,328 --> 00:08:15,607
Please enlighten me.

134
00:08:16,648 --> 00:08:18,047
You're lying,

135
00:08:18,568 --> 00:08:20,047
and every word is a trap.

136
00:08:21,288 --> 00:08:22,727
What do you mean?

137
00:08:23,328 --> 00:08:24,607
It was just a chance encounter!

138
00:08:25,128 --> 00:08:26,647
Like you and me right now.

139
00:08:30,728 --> 00:08:31,687
Right now,

140
00:08:32,928 --> 00:08:34,327
what exactly are we?

141
00:08:38,128 --> 00:08:38,807
What are you doing?

142
00:08:39,328 --> 00:08:40,487
Let go, Zhou Yichen!

143
00:08:40,928 --> 00:08:42,047
I'm your dad's concubine!

144
00:08:42,168 --> 00:08:43,287
If others see this,

145
00:08:43,288 --> 00:08:43,847
what will they think?

146
00:08:43,848 --> 00:08:45,327
Then let them all see, so be it!

147
00:08:46,488 --> 00:08:47,647
You watch opera with my brother,

148
00:08:47,648 --> 00:08:48,567
you share Father's bed at night,

149
00:08:48,568 --> 00:08:50,047
and you meet Captain Yu in secret by day!

150
00:08:50,568 --> 00:08:51,767
Why can they,

151
00:08:52,888 --> 00:08:53,687
but I can't?

152
00:08:53,888 --> 00:08:54,927
What are you talking about?

153
00:08:55,488 --> 00:08:56,327
There has been absolutely

154
00:08:56,408 --> 00:08:57,247
no impropriety between Zhou Yimo,

155
00:08:57,248 --> 00:08:58,527
Captain Yu, and me.

156
00:08:58,808 --> 00:09:00,407
But look what you're doing now.

157
00:09:00,848 --> 00:09:02,127
Then let them all see.

158
00:09:04,088 --> 00:09:04,687
Better yet, let the police

159
00:09:04,688 --> 00:09:05,847
arrest us all.

160
00:09:06,648 --> 00:09:07,727
Then they can ask

161
00:09:08,648 --> 00:09:10,527
why you would rather avoid me

162
00:09:10,888 --> 00:09:12,767
than meet an outsider like Captain Yu.

163
00:09:13,648 --> 00:09:14,807
At this point,

164
00:09:15,288 --> 00:09:16,927
I can only play along with it.

165
00:09:25,408 --> 00:09:27,407
Why do I avoid you but not them?

166
00:09:28,768 --> 00:09:30,287
Why don't you reflect on yourself?

167
00:09:31,368 --> 00:09:32,927
Because you're not good enough!

168
00:09:38,968 --> 00:09:40,047
When I'm with you,

169
00:09:40,408 --> 00:09:41,407
it's not like being with them—

170
00:09:41,408 --> 00:09:42,927
happy, relaxed, and free.

171
00:09:43,528 --> 00:09:45,207
Don't you understand such a simple thing?

172
00:09:48,408 --> 00:09:49,287
Am I not good?

173
00:09:53,088 --> 00:09:54,727
Don't look for problems in others.

174
00:09:55,648 --> 00:09:57,207
Instead, reflect more on yourself.

175
00:10:05,688 --> 00:10:05,967
-

176
00:10:10,088 --> 00:10:11,087
An He,

177
00:10:11,088 --> 00:10:12,367
hurry up.

178
00:10:12,368 --> 00:10:13,607
Don't make me wait.

179
00:10:15,728 --> 00:10:16,367
Don't move.

180
00:10:16,488 --> 00:10:17,167
Fifth concubine of the Zhou family,

181
00:10:17,168 --> 00:10:21,607
are you always this rude?

182
00:10:21,608 --> 00:10:22,607
You know me?

183
00:10:24,208 --> 00:10:25,807
You came to ask me about something?

184
00:10:26,928 --> 00:10:27,967
Ye Xiaoman.

185
00:10:30,288 --> 00:10:31,087
How did you know?

186
00:10:31,568 --> 00:10:32,647
I recognized you.

187
00:10:33,648 --> 00:10:35,287
Years ago, your sister showed me a

188
00:10:35,288 --> 00:10:36,447
photo of you from school.

189
00:10:37,128 --> 00:10:38,047
That night at the theater,

190
00:10:38,048 --> 00:10:39,447
I recognized you immediately.

191
00:10:45,928 --> 00:10:47,607
I know you didn't kill my sister.

192
00:10:48,048 --> 00:10:48,807
Of course.

193
00:10:49,528 --> 00:10:50,807
Everyone here

194
00:10:52,528 --> 00:10:54,287
held her closest to their hearts.

195
00:10:56,808 --> 00:10:58,287
So you're the Liu Mengmei

196
00:10:58,968 --> 00:11:01,127
my sister mentioned her soulmate?

197
00:11:03,848 --> 00:11:05,847
I paid today,

198
00:11:06,168 --> 00:11:09,087
so An He must accompany me.

199
00:11:09,808 --> 00:11:12,807
An He!

200
00:11:12,848 --> 00:11:13,967
Open the door!

201
00:11:13,968 --> 00:11:14,767
An He!

202
00:11:15,368 --> 00:11:16,327
Come down.

203
00:11:16,528 --> 00:11:17,607
I'll catch you.

204
00:11:17,968 --> 00:11:19,047
But it's too high.

205
00:11:19,648 --> 00:11:20,607
Trust me,

206
00:11:20,688 --> 00:11:21,967
and trust yourself.

207
00:11:48,848 --> 00:11:50,567
As those society sees as the lowest class,

208
00:11:50,728 --> 00:11:52,407
our lives are already humble and hard.

209
00:11:52,528 --> 00:11:54,247
Why are you always so happy?

210
00:11:54,488 --> 00:11:55,767
Because I have a dream.

211
00:11:56,528 --> 00:11:57,847
What's your dream?

212
00:11:58,528 --> 00:11:59,247
Freedom.

213
00:12:00,408 --> 00:12:01,127
An He,

214
00:12:01,408 --> 00:12:02,567
do you yearn for freedom?

215
00:12:03,288 --> 00:12:04,407
What is freedom?

216
00:12:05,288 --> 00:12:06,847
It feels like this moment.

217
00:12:07,448 --> 00:12:08,567
We're just ourselves—

218
00:12:08,888 --> 00:12:09,927
not someone's servant,

219
00:12:10,088 --> 00:12:10,967
not a theater star.

220
00:12:11,488 --> 00:12:12,287
No need to be beautiful,

221
00:12:12,528 --> 00:12:13,367
no need to be obedient,

222
00:12:13,648 --> 00:12:14,527
no need to be compliant.

223
00:12:14,808 --> 00:12:15,767
Freedom of thought,

224
00:12:16,008 --> 00:12:16,807
freedom of dress,

225
00:12:17,048 --> 00:12:17,847
freedom to love.

226
00:12:18,128 --> 00:12:18,887
Financial freedom.

227
00:12:19,488 --> 00:12:20,487
Will that day ever come?

228
00:12:20,848 --> 00:12:21,567
It will.

229
00:12:23,608 --> 00:12:24,727
She had such a vibrant spirit.

230
00:12:26,288 --> 00:12:27,247
I never imagined

231
00:12:28,808 --> 00:12:30,407
it would lead to

232
00:12:30,408 --> 00:12:31,327
such a quiet, dark end.

233
00:12:33,368 --> 00:12:34,647
My sister didn't commit suicide.

234
00:12:35,368 --> 00:12:36,447
Someone took her life.

235
00:12:36,768 --> 00:12:37,767
Why do you say that?

236
00:12:39,048 --> 00:12:40,247
I got the autopsy report.

237
00:12:41,328 --> 00:12:43,087
It nearly burned at the police station.

238
00:12:44,408 --> 00:12:45,407
Before she died,

239
00:12:45,888 --> 00:12:47,887
she was assaulted by several people,

240
00:12:48,528 --> 00:12:50,527
then thrown into the pond to drown.

241
00:12:51,208 --> 00:12:52,367
She never considered

242
00:12:52,368 --> 00:12:53,527
taking her own life.

243
00:13:03,128 --> 00:13:03,887
So

244
00:13:05,768 --> 00:13:07,207
you married into the Zhou family

245
00:13:08,168 --> 00:13:09,207
to uncover the truth?

246
00:13:09,768 --> 00:13:10,327
Yes.

247
00:13:11,048 --> 00:13:11,927
Even if I die,

248
00:13:12,288 --> 00:13:13,407
I must find the truth.

249
00:13:16,848 --> 00:13:17,647
Who do you suspect?

250
00:13:18,288 --> 00:13:19,047
Zhou Yimo.

251
00:13:19,528 --> 00:13:20,287
Zhou Yichen.

252
00:13:21,048 --> 00:13:22,047
Not Zhou Yimo.

253
00:13:22,848 --> 00:13:23,647
Why?

254
00:13:24,528 --> 00:13:25,767
Based on my knowledge of his character,

255
00:13:25,768 --> 00:13:26,887
it couldn't possibly be him.

256
00:13:29,528 --> 00:13:30,887
The eldest Zhou son

257
00:13:31,328 --> 00:13:33,407
has a reputation for being unrestrained.

258
00:13:34,408 --> 00:13:35,687
Rare to have a confidante like you

259
00:13:35,688 --> 00:13:36,527
so supportive of him.

260
00:13:36,528 --> 00:13:37,287
You've misunderstood.

261
00:13:37,968 --> 00:13:39,567
When we met frequently years ago,

262
00:13:39,968 --> 00:13:41,327
it was to help your sister escape.

263
00:13:41,408 --> 00:13:43,167
Second concubine was aggressive,

264
00:13:43,168 --> 00:13:44,527
always hurting your sister.

265
00:13:45,288 --> 00:13:46,327
So he made excuses

266
00:13:46,328 --> 00:13:47,407
to take her to the opera

267
00:13:47,648 --> 00:13:49,207
all to help your sister

268
00:13:49,648 --> 00:13:51,207
avoid countless abuses.

269
00:13:55,128 --> 00:13:55,807
Really?

270
00:13:58,328 --> 00:13:59,447
As for Zhou Yichen...

271
00:14:04,448 --> 00:14:05,407
What about Zhou Yichen?

272
00:14:06,688 --> 00:14:07,527
I'd rather not say.

273
00:14:10,248 --> 00:14:10,767
Miss An,

274
00:14:10,768 --> 00:14:11,607
are you ready?

275
00:14:11,728 --> 00:14:12,887
Don't keep the Marshal waiting.

276
00:14:13,728 --> 00:14:14,407
I've got something to take care of.

277
00:14:14,648 --> 00:14:15,407
I must leave.

278
00:14:15,728 --> 00:14:16,487
Wait!

279
00:14:18,048 --> 00:14:18,967
Since you and my sister

280
00:14:19,968 --> 00:14:21,167
were so close,

281
00:14:23,288 --> 00:14:24,687
why did you cut ties?

282
00:14:27,528 --> 00:14:28,607
That's personal.

283
00:14:29,728 --> 00:14:30,447
Anyway

284
00:14:31,408 --> 00:14:32,287
it wasn't her fault.

285
00:14:33,168 --> 00:14:34,207
Everyone has secrets.

286
00:14:34,288 --> 00:14:35,167
I respect that.

287
00:14:35,488 --> 00:14:36,767
If these matters

288
00:14:37,168 --> 00:14:38,407
relate to my sister's death,

289
00:14:38,528 --> 00:14:39,447
then I'm sorry.

290
00:14:41,168 --> 00:14:42,887
I will uncover the truth.

291
00:14:49,968 --> 00:14:51,047
What is freedom?

292
00:14:51,848 --> 00:14:53,407
This feeling right now.

293
00:14:54,048 --> 00:14:55,007
We're just ourselves.

294
00:14:55,528 --> 00:14:56,527
Not slaves to any family,

295
